Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro turned out to be a troublesome relic that could be activated regardless of the location or season.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, Academy City will be conquered by the Roman Church at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:26.46,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(670,849)\pos(824,528)}#13 Croce di Pietro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a convenient place to put your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to get dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.86,0:01:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time for you to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.43,0:01:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want to spend a stimulating night with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need one more edge in this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its form is that of a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear. Devour my body to gain strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocentius!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Innocentius!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortis931...{official}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prove to them why my name is the strongest!{see http://www12.atwiki.jp/index-index/pages/211.html}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.07,0:02:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashes to ashes, dust to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire killer, crimson cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, you lame magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocentius!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell how they're moving like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need an absolute basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that no one else will suffer misfortune because of differences in values.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win and reach an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.71,0:03:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Basis104.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opponent is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many people do you have to hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt anyone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have an objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I crush you, my mission's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro and Roman Church will make the perfect world for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of objective is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking so arrogantly when you're just watching others do the work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the work for me, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't really care who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just has to group up the various principles and ideas of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to protect that basis no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get those kind of complicated arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just give into such a stupid request like handing over Academy City and everyone in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that because you don't know, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen someone just stand there in shock at what is occurring in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never heard someone simply say, "It hurts."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, that's no reason to attack Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't justify using someone as a stepping stone for someone else's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issues you're having are things that everyone feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone fails, and sometimes they fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you fall, you can just stand back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you look miserable, even if everything doesn't go as planned, you have to stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just throw away someone else's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will you choose, Oriana Thomson?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you failed once, are you going to let others do things for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they failed, are you going to lend those failures a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ending this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I state this to all of the abilities in my body:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unleash your full potential, and destroy the target in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you put even a little effort into making this festival a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bit of a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is beyond my expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all trying to protect the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back at your hospital room before the Night Parade starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So wait for me, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the mark of my determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm just going to let that all go to waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me, go for the Croce di Pietro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make Oriana reveal where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it from activating...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will end soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro will soon activate, and Academy City will be put under the Roman Catholic Church's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to just get rid of people like us who get in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We grieve over your wounds and wish to heal them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, only if we can determine that doing so will profit the Roman Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't argue with her, Kamijou Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia should be close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cross, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should clarify.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro is not in Academy City at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}At its peak, the area of Roman Catholic Church revival affected by the Croce di Pietro was 47,000 square kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to assume that it'll easily cover the entirety of Academy City even if it's activated outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana was just a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate that she was defeated, but the Croce di Pietro will turn even that into a beneficial situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only point that is of concern to us now is that science will bow to religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By denying science and showing our power, we will show the power of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Searching and attacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado can't use magic twice in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not destroy Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:10:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we make you throw away the cult of science, we will embrace you as loving comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:00.95,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Call Tsuchimikado
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him use his search magic to calculate Lidvia's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use my communication spell, we can leave it to the forces outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.73,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro will change the world in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,107 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some trump card to turn this situation around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spell used by the constellations in the night sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gathering starlight on the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many points outside of Academy City are there that can cover all of Academy City?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the furthest point matching those criteria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The northern perimeter of Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 1700 meters out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&Hfef6ed&\fs35\blur1\fax0.1\bord0\shad0\pos(641,167)\frz38.797}Daihaseisai Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 more seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it's the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is the end, then it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think so Lidvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I destroyed your illusion, I couldn't even keep the promise I made with my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current time is exactly 6:30pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In case you didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when the Night Parade starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this much light, the stars can be blotted out easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lost to the light that everyone protecting the Daihaseisai created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have figured out who the main character of the Daihaseisai is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally I think you should destroy the Croce di Pietro and promise not to bother Academy City anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have forgotten that I am a devout member of the Roman Catholic Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess you're going to be running around in a game of tag, just like a sports festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia Lorenzetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You engaged in a battle that may have determined the fate of Academy City and the world without letting me know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and on top of that, you got hospitalized after getting beaten up by a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Index-san, whenever I mention magic you always come stumbling right into the middle of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, that makes it sound like I'm really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you never noticed shows that you're a real—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My my, what a delightful scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a serious talk here, so get out, short hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary citizens are allowed to cooperate in Judgment's peacekeeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama, you do realize this is a hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see today's final results?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our school sailed right past yours into first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you haven't forgotten about our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I can't do anything like that with my body in this condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Oriana Thompson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all those poor lost sinners. {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem, attention please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Archbishop of the Church of England, Laura Stewart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now that I've introduced myself, you can't ignore me. Right, Milady Lidvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find me in this private jet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had them slap a little present onto the wall of your plane at Haneda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite creepy, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That personality of yours where you laugh harder the more you're pressured...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything you can do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The harsher the pain, the sweeter the joy will be upon overcoming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must give thanks to the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The taller a wall is, the greater the satisfaction upon getting over it, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is some truth in what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you little animal at the edge of a cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidvia, I don't mind saving you if you give up on Rome's teachings and lick my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe you and that thing can make a crater.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Croce di Pietro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this speed of descent I should make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I definitely will make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what makes it fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Lidvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will you pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful spiritual tool in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the lost and pitiful servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greater the challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the greater the satisfaction once you trample over me, the creator of the challenge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will trample...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over that unreachable flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite the tremor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development of the key, Imagine Breaker, is still unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I be able to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have to consider the possibility of taking action myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sleeping on the bench in the waiting room,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they told me I can't use it in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bed is so nice and soft...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The frog doctor said I can leave tomorrow or the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look kind of sad, Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he go do something reckless again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, I haven't heard all the details yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently the Roman Catholic magicians tried to take advantage of the Daihaseisai to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, without saying a single word to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he went on a huge rampage and only told me about it like he was making a report after it all happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll help out anyone in need...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I shouldn't have been saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all I do is cause trouble for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma seems to enjoy spending time with you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Fukiyose-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind hospital visit is this, suddenly slapping me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would be surprised seeing a naked boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who barged in while I was in the middle of changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked him, he said it was for his own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's what happiness is for Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For better or for worse, Index and I suddenly find ourselves headed for Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.96,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we might as well relax and look at the sights!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is that Orsola?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Amakusa Church too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: "City of Water."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, this epic will begin!
